          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 10,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Keqing_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "刻晴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "刻晴突破增加暴擊傷害，與該武器的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "副詞綴互補，能減少聖遺物的壓力。該武器的技能也比較契合重擊流刻晴。缺點是精煉難度較大，和高精煉匣裡龍吟比起來，精1黑劍的期望上限會略低，但對刻晴來說是四星武器中較優的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 27,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Jean_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "琴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "雙風體系中，琴充當著副C兼奶的位置，傷害來源只有元素戰技/爆發，而琴的這兩個技能的攻擊頻率極低（只有一下），那麼",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "就顯得比較重要了，選擇該武器的原因只是為了其",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "副詞綴，若沒有其他能使用黑劍的角色，給琴或許是一個不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 31,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kamisato Ayato_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "神里綾人",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器是神里綾人在四星武器中較為不錯的選擇，提高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "的同時也提升了普通攻擊的傷害。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 9,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kaeya_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "凱亞",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能為物理普攻流凱亞提供普攻/重擊的傷害提升，回覆血量的特效與凱亞的天賦4相輔相成也能增加駐場輸出的生存能力。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
